channel.title: Webclient Problem
channel.description:
Hello,
Recently I have made my own Project Insanity webclient, I have an auto-extracting cache which is ZIPPED correctly. Now, I have made it a .jar file and it opens perfectly in my desktop (downloaded version) but when I try and put it into a HTML and put it on a website it just get stuck on "Requesting Title Screen".
Now, I don't know why it does this as it works on my computer as a .jar file when I open it. Please could you help me out!
Thanks,
Zudore.
